Audio CD (May 29, 2006)
Original Release Date: 1996
Number of Discs: 1
Format: EP, Import
Label: Century Media

Description

Freedom Call is an EP released after Holy Land, featuring one new song in the title track. Remixed versions of "Queen of the Night," "Reaching Horizons," and "Deep Blue" are all right, but are not too different from the previously available versions. The orchestral version of "Stand Away" is excellent, and a remake of Judas Priest&#039;s "Painkiller" is the other high point of this EP. [Freedom Call was reissued by Century Media in 1999.]
